，没有剧本，模拟如何击退中国的进攻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:17:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-starts-annual-war-games-aiming-closely-mimic-actual-combat-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，失火油轮进入马来西亚FPSO Bertam码头区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fire-hit-oil-tanker-enters-malaysia-fpso-bertam-terminal-area-data-shows-2024-07-22/</link><description>伦敦证券交易所集团 (LSEG) 和 Kpler 的航运数据显示，超级油轮 Ceres I 在周日被地方当局拦截后，于周一早上进入马来西亚 Bertam 浮动油码头区域。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fire-hit-oil-tanker-enters-malaysia-fpso-bertam-terminal-area-data-shows-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车与大众成立项目公司推出新的电动汽车架构</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-volkswagen-set-up-project-house-roll-out-new-ev-architecture-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国电动汽车（EV）制造商小鹏汽车周一表示，已与德国汽车制造商大众汽车公司合作建立了工程师项目室，以加快新电动汽车架构的开发进程。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-volkswagen-set-up-project-house-roll-out-new-ev-architecture-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着拜登结束连任竞选，美元走软；降息后人民币持稳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-biden-ends-reelection-bid-yuan-steady-after-rate-cut-2024-07-22/</link><description>美元周一下跌，是对美国总统乔·拜登决定结束连任竞选的最初反应，为另一位民主党人挑战唐纳德·特朗普扫清了道路。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-biden-ends-reelection-bid-yuan-steady-after-rate-cut-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>部长表示，菲律宾正在考虑与法国、加拿大和新西兰签署防务协定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-eyes-defence-pacts-with-france-canada-nz-minister-says-2024-07-22/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周一表示，菲律宾正在寻求与加拿大、法国、新西兰和其他国家达成互惠的部队准入协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:43:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-eyes-defence-pacts-with-france-canada-nz-minister-says-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国意外降息以支持经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-cuts-short-term-policy-rate-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国周一降低了关键的短期政策利率和基准贷款利率，此举令市场感到意外，以期促进世界第二大经济体的增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:26:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-cuts-short-term-policy-rate-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国降息，亚洲股市下滑；拜登退出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-22/</link><description>亚洲股市周一再次下跌，中国央行意外降息几乎没有带来什么提振，而在美国总统乔·拜登决定退出竞选后，华尔街期货走强。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:22:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国对冲基金准备迎接严厉新规定带来的剧变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-hedge-funds-brace-upheaval-tough-new-rules-2024-07-21/</link><description>中国价值7150亿美元的对冲基金行业正面临下个月生效的严格监管带来的新压力，迫使一些投资公司向白衣骑士寻求新资金，甚至关门歇业。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 23:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-hedge-funds-brace-upheaval-tough-new-rules-2024-07-21/</guid></item><item><title>独家：流向俄罗斯的非法芯片流量放缓，但中国、香港仍然是转运中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/illicit-chip-flows-russia-seen-slowing-china-hong-kong-remain-transshipment-hubs-2024-07-21/</link><description>美国商务部此前未披露的数据显示，今年通过中国和香港运送的用于推动俄罗斯战争的半导体和其他受限制货物减少了五分之一，但香港仍然是全球逃避制裁的热点。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/illicit-chip-flows-russia-seen-slowing-china-hong-kong-remain-transshipment-hubs-2024-07-21/</guid></item><item><title>期待已久的中国政策更新并未出现重大转变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-publishes-policy-agenda-with-few-implementation-details-2024-07-21/</link><description>由于中国面临贸易紧张、通货紧缩、房地产危机、债务激增以及消费者和企业信心疲软，一些经济学家希望情况会有所改变。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:02:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-publishes-policy-agenda-with-few-implementation-details-2024-07-21/</guid></item><item><title>马尼拉称，中国和菲律宾就南海补给任务的“临时安排”达成一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-resupply-ship-south-china-sea-shoal-without-us-help-2024-07-21/</link><description>去年，有争议水道的紧张局势已升级为暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 09:46:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-resupply-ship-south-china-sea-shoal-without-us-help-2024-07-21/</guid></item><item><title>总统表示，台湾必须保护自己的主权，了解自己的历史</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-must-protect-its-sovereignty-know-its-own-history-president-says-2024-07-21/</link><description>周日，台湾总统赖清德表示，台湾必须保护自己的主权，了解自己的文化和历史，他否认了之前关于台湾可以作为“收复”中国的基地的错误看法。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 07:33:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-must-protect-its-sovereignty-know-its-own-history-president-says-2024-07-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>